{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"08df9879-2ae4-4f23-9c16-839ad280f3c4","content":"There's no workflow file in the current directory, so here's a general guide for the migration:\n\n### Key Changes for NuGet Trusted Publishing (OIDC)\n\n**1. Add `permissions` to your job:**\n```yaml\npermissions:\n  id-token: write   # Required for OIDC token request\n  contents: read\n```\n\n**2. Replace the `dotnet nuget push` step:**\n\nBefore (API key):\n```yaml\n- run: dotnet nuget push **/*.nupkg --api-key ${{ secrets.NUGET_API_KEY }} --source https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n```\n\nAfter (trusted publishing):\n```yaml\n- run: dotnet nuget push **/*.nupkg --source https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n```\n\nNo `--api-key` needed — the OIDC token is used automatically.\n\n**3. Configure NuGet.org side:**\n- Go to **nuget.org → Manage Packages → your package → Trusted Publishers**\n- Add a new GitHub Actions trusted publisher with your **repository owner**, **repo name**, **workflow filename**, and optionally an **environment name**.\n\n**4. (Recommended) Use a GitHub environment:**\n```yaml\njobs:\n  publish:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    environment: nuget-publish   # matches what you register on nuget.org\n    permissions:\n      id-token: write\n      contents: read\n```\n\nThis adds an approval gate and scopes the OIDC token.\n\n**5. Remove the `NUGET_API_KEY` secret** from your repo once everything works.\n\n---\n\n**Summary:** The code change is small — add `id-token: write` permission and drop `--api-key`. The main setup is on **nuget.org** where you register your repo as a trusted publisher.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"c7512aa1-e5a1-4d50-a3cb-1383a365fc38","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"There's no repository content here. The user is asking a general question about switching from NuGet API key-based publishing to NuGet trusted publishing (OIDC) in GitHub Actions. I'll provide guidance based on my knowledge.","outputTokens":503,"requestId":"C00D:1BCB52:125E62:15DDAD:69EABE91"},"id":"87648dd1-42f8-4ecd-8f72-fac44f98503a","timestamp":"2026-04-24T00:51:41.678Z","parentId":"4cb311bd-ff78-4687-9bd8-aa0849c3d708"}
